data.description: Home sweet home! This home is centrally located. It’s near schools, freeways, hospitals and shopping.  This One level 4-3 spacious floor plan with a mother-in law suite on the opposite side of home has quite a few updates. The plumbing was updated in 2021, lighting, ceiling fans, HVAC 2021, hot water heater 2023, electrical panel in 2020, converted the formal living to a study 2020, updated master bath and guest bathroom, updated fireplace & Installed granite in all the wet areas in 2020.  Installed a privacy fence and replaced concrete on patio in 2021.  Foundation work done in 2021 as well.  The  owner is a licensed realtor. Show and sell.
